reviewText: this is a great collection of torchic episodes it is fun and enjoyable to watch. if you have not seen this dvd then I recommend you do.
I LOVE TORCHIC. IT IS THE BEST POKEMON. EXCEPT MAYBE AEGISLASH, BUT HE'S NOT ON THIS DVD, SO IT'S NOT A 6/5. 5/5 IS STILL GOOD THOUGH.

What can be better then seeing pollo (torchic) as i call it, in all its glory.

Nothing in the world is better then torchic expect maybe 2 torchics.

I highly reccomend this pokemon dvd to any torchic fan.

get IT. changed my life.
